name: my malevolent matriarch
description:
she hurts me so, even to the point of torture, miscast and loss of fortune, and yet every few nights, i feel i have to go back out

-

november 14th, 2021

sitting in a dark room
street lights silhouette through
shuddered blinds. lines of
synthetic sunshine encapsulate
my face; the city,
the streets,
she calls to me.

--

@literallynft
